  m_Text: "Feature:\r\nHigh Quality. Professional Straight Razor.\r Foldable and
    mini size, suitable for carrying or travel use.\r Sharp stainless steel blade,
    easy and quick to shave beards. \rIdeal for barber shops & hair salons use or
    personal use.\r Hollow design is conducive to dry razor after use and inhibit
    bacterial growth."
