  - {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1e1ca856ab8754f439c726982e7a713c, type: 3}
  SottotitoliTesti:
  - "Hey there, welcome to virtual barbershop\u2019s tutorial! Here you\u2019ll learn
    all the basics to start your business."
  - Your work day is about to start, so make the most out of this time to get ready
    for the day, to make purchases or to improve the furnishing.
  - If you want to skip prep time just ring the highlighted bell on the counter.
  - Your first client is here!
  - Try to create the same haircut as the one portrayed in the highlighted photo.
    If the icons below the photograph are on, it means additional products need to
    be used.
  - The timer above the bell will show you how much time is left. As soon as the
    time runs out, it will be kept count of all progress made up until then.
  - "Keep in mind though, that with a wrong haircut you don\u2019t just risk not
    getting paid, you risk losing your reputation!"
  - Let's start, open the drawer, grab the electric shaver and press the "Trigger"
    button to turn it on or off.
  - You finished your first haircut.
  - Remember that a fine shop stands out also thanks to its decor.
  - "Behind the counter you\u2019ll find a computer, you can navigate the desktop
    by grabbing the mouse."
  - "Press \u201CA\u201D on your controller to click on the store icon, then buy
    an ornament and wait for the courier to arrive."
  - Your order is here! Take the purchased item out of the box and place it in a
    pretty visible point of the room.
  - Good job!
  - If you want, you can throw away items you no longer have use for. Just grab them
    and release them in the trash can.
  - Try throwing away the highlighted object for example.
  - "Well done! Keep in mind that you must get 5 stars out of all the rating categories
    in order to achieve the \u201CBarber of the Year\u201D prize."
  - "You can check the shop\u2019s status on the computer through the Advisor app."
  - Well, tutorial is done! But you can come back here whenever you want.
  - See you soon!
